---
import { Activity } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 overflow-hidden border-b border-white/5">
  
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-background">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-[500px] bg-brand-cyan/5 blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
    
    <a href="https://status.arkaniahost.xyz" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded border border-green-500/20 bg-green-500/5 hover:bg-green-500/10 transition-colors mb-8 cursor-pointer group">
      <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
        <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-green-500 opacity-75"></span>
        <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-green-500"></span>
      </span>
      <span class="text-xs font-mono font-bold text-green-400 tracking-widest uppercase group-hover:text-green-300">
        Estado de la Red: Estable
      </span>
    </a>

    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tight mb-6">
      ¿Necesitas <span class="text-gradient">Ayuda?</span>
    </h1>
    
    <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Antes de contactar a soporte, te recomendamos revisar el protocolo de diagnóstico. 
      La mayoría de las incidencias se resuelven en minutos.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>